the expression of the emotions in man an.data-term: the expression of the emotions in man and animals

examples.en: John yawned and scratched his leg.
She yawned and rubbed her eyes.
The pit yawned open in front of them.
The child yawned during the long performance.
examples.ru: Ребенок зевал во время этого долгого выступления.

examples.en: He yawned, closed his eyes again, and turned over.
examples.ru: Зевнув, он снова закрыл глаза и перевернулся на другой бок.

examples.en: Carl sat up in bed, yawned, and stretched.
examples.ru: Карл сел в постели, зевнул и потянулся.
